{"tid":1796491,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄧炳強促暴徒收手還香港平安","createTime":"2019-12-24T15:58:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T18:26:34.000Z","uid":133680,"like":22,"dislike":227,"uniUserReply":98,"replies":[{"pid":"eefe9831ecda59c588ac6df53678f781737f3653","tid":1796491,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T15:58:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1069522\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1069522&d=nB3K3ojK8rN8kNU4dsXAYylkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=98045e07\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1069522&h=37256632\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1069522</a><br />\n<br />\n（獨媒特約報導）警務處處長鄧炳強在晚上7時15分到達尖沙咀廣東道一帶巡視，並與在場戒備的防暴警察及交通警逐一握手問候，警察公共關係科總警司郭嘉銓及公共關係科高級警司江永祥江永祥亦有現身陪同「出巡」，有市民在旁高呼「死黑警」。<br />\n<br />\n鄧炳強之後會見記者，表示自己是特意前來感謝同事守護香港。他主動提及香港罪案數字上升，指是自6月起暴徒破壞香港，令罪案急升，又批評市民守法意識薄弱縱容罪行，令劫匪都開始「打爛舖頭」，使爆竊案及行劫案上升。<br />\n<br />\n被問及大批防暴警察於尖沙咀高姿態戒備，會否影響節日氣氛。鄧炳強反指影響節日氣氛的是暴徒，「只要暴徒唔出嚟，我哋係唔洗番工」，並促暴徒「收手」，還香港市民一個真正的平安夜。"},{"pid":"7600865e09c5167e6aea579e1b971595a600868c","tid":1796491,"uid":67348,"like":62,"dislike":1,"score":61,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T15:59:29.000Z","msg":"佢地就唔洗番工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"520e1b1e50826aef33ec9631abbaf00a76dcbffc","tid":1796491,"uid":164838,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T15:59:41.000Z","msg":"已讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"746a524faba687c36a68748fd9a8934409dcdf3c","tid":1796491,"uid":165840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T15:59:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj